The YUV420 to RGB24 conversion routine in src/jpeg.c is taken from libv4l,
written by Hans de Goede (j.w.r.degoede <aT> hhs.nl). libv4l can be downloaded
from the Video4Linux Mercurial repository at http://linuxtv.org/hg/v4l-dvb
More information and instructions can be found at http://www.linuxtv.org/repo/

The tinyjpeg library used in the JPEG/MJPEG to RGB24 conversion routine in 
rgb.c, is written by Luc Saillard, and can be downloaded from
http://www.saillard.org/programs_and_patches/tinyjpegdecoder/

